["<div dir=\"rtl\" align=\"right\">\n\n\n <table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: -52.65pt\" dir=\"rtl\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n  <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   وَ فِي قَبْضِ كَفِّ الطِّفْلِ عِنْدَ وُلُودِهِ </td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">دَلِيلٌ \n عَلَى الْحِرْصِ الْمُرَكَّبِ فِي الْحَيِ</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">وَ فِي \n بَسْطِهَا عِنْدَ الْمَمَاتِ مَوَاعِظُ</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">أَلَا \n فَانْظُرُونِي قَدْ خَرَجْتُ بِلَا شَيْ‏ء</td>\n  </tr>\n    </table>\n  \n</div>","ديوان الإمام علي(ع)"]